---
// Our Approach section for Healthcare industry page
---

<section id="approach" class="cre-approach-section">
  <div class="cre-approach-container">
    <span class="section-label">OUR APPROACH FOR HEALTHCARE</span>
    <h2 class="cre-approach-headline">
      Purpose-built systems for patient velocity
    </h2>
    <p class="cre-approach-intro">
      We don't build generic healthcare software and force it into your workflow. We architect systems specifically for how healthcare organizations operate—from patient intake through clinical care coordination. Every feature is designed to eliminate friction and accelerate patient throughput without sacrificing quality or safety.
    </p>

    <!-- Image Grid -->
    <div class="cre-approach-images-grid">
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-website-pic-dashboard.webp" 
          alt="Patient velocity infrastructure"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-dashboard-9.webp" 
          alt="Intelligent automation"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="cre-approach-image-item">
        <img 
          src="/logos/intelio-7.webp" 
          alt="Ownership and control"
          class="cre-approach-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Text Cards Grid -->
    <div class="cre-approach-cards-grid">
      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Patient velocity infrastructure</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We build unified platforms that connect your entire patient journey—from intake through discharge. Every system is designed to reduce time-to-care, not just store data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Intelligent automation</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          We embed AI and automation into your core workflows—automating patient intake, verifying insurance in real-time, generating clinical documentation, and surfacing quality issues—so your team focuses on care, not data entry.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="cre-approach-card">
        <h3 class="cre-approach-card-title">Ownership and control</h3>
        <p class="cre-approach-card-description">
          You own the systems we build. No vendor lock-in, no subscription dependencies. We architect for long-term ownership, giving you the flexibility to evolve as your organization grows.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-approach-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-approach-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-approach-intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  /* Image Grid */
  .cre-approach-images-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cre-approach-image-item {
    width: 100%;
    height: 280px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cre-approach-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-approach-image-item:hover .cre-approach-image {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  /* Text Cards Grid */
  .cre-approach-cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-approach-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .cre-approach-card-title {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .cre-approach-card-description {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-approach-images-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .cre-approach-image-item {
      height: 240px;
    }

    .cre-approach-cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-approach-section {
      padding: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-approach-images-grid {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .cre-approach-image-item {
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>

